dct_title_s: Germaniae: post omnes in hoc forma; Claes Janssen Visscher.; Germania;Germany
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Border of map includes views of cities, costumes, and arms of German principalities. Illustrations include cherubs with fruit and a chalice around the title cartouche and ships on the ocean. From "Atlantis maioris appendix", Johannes Janssonius, 1630. 1 map; 34 x 46 cm.
dct_rights_sm: This map is in the public domain.
